# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Secrets — NEVER commit. Real values live in the platform secret
# manager (Vercel env / GitHub secrets); pull locally on demand
# with `vercel env pull .env.local`. Only *.example / *.template track.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
env.local
env.dev
!.env.example
!.env.production.template
!env.example
setup_vercel_env.py
setup_vercel_env.bat
vercel_env_setup_commands.txt

